long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows you to stream music from WBOR 91.1FM, providing commercial-free radio from Bowdoin College, Brunswick, ME, since 1951. Control music streaming and see information about what's playing right from your browser.

For assistance using the app or to report bugs, email rmartin[AT]bowdoin.edu
